an data-text=\"divi\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">DIVI</span>❦<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Nervae\"><span data-text=\"Nervae\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">NERVAE</span></span></span>❦<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>❦<span data-text=\"filius\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"\">F</span>❦<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Nerva\"><span data-text=\"Nerva\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"\">NERVA</span></span>❦<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Traianus\"><span data-text=\"Traianus\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"\">TRAIANUS</span></span>❦<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Augustus\"><span data-text=\"Augustus\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"\">AUG</span></span>❦<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Germanicus\"><span data-text=\"Germanicus\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"\">GERMANICUS</span></span>❦<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Dacicus\"><span data-text=\"Dacicus\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"\">DACICUS</span></span></span>❦<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"pontifex\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"\">PONTIFEX</span><span data-text=\"maximus\" data-n=\"115\" data-lemma=\"\">MAXIMUS</span>❦<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"tribunicia\" data-n=\"125\" data-lemma=\"\">TR</span>❦<span data-text=\"potestate\" data-n=\"135\" data-lemma=\"\">POT</span>❦<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">VII</span>❦<span data-text=\"imperator\" data-n=\"150\" data-lemma=\"\">IMP</span>❦<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">IIII</span>❦<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-text=\"consul\" data-n=\"165\" data-lemma=\"\">COS</span>❦V❦<span data-text=\"pater\" data-n=\"180\" data-lemma=\"\">P</span>❦<span data-text=\"patriae\" data-n=\"190\" data