      "id": "translation",
      "html": "<h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0009-0009-2753-4014\">Alfredo Tosques</a></p>  <p>Emperor Caesar, son of the deified Nerva, Nerva Trajan Augustus Germanicus Dacicus, Pontifex Maximus, holding tribunician power for the seventh time, acclaimed imperator for the fourth time, consul for the fifth time, father of the fatherland.</p>  "
